main event: A civilian pilot observed four metallic discs flying in formation over Malibu Beach, California on January 22, 2023.
interesting points: The objects were flying at an estimated altitude of 20,000 feet., The speed of the objects was estimated at 1200 mph., The observation lasted for 5 minutes., The conclusion from the report was that the objects were probably aircraft., The objects were described as being metallic and disc-shaped.
